   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 数据探索与分析\\n",
    "\\n",
    "本Notebook用于探索媒体数据采集、清洗与基础统计分析。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys\\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, '..')\\n",
    "\\n",
    "from src.data.cleaner import DataCleaner\\n",
    "from src.data.chunker import TextChunker\\n",
    "from src.nlp.ner import NERExtractor"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 初始化工具\\n",
    "cleaner = DataCleaner(min_content_length=50)\\n",
    "chunker = TextChunker(max_chunk_size=2000)\\n",
    "ner = NERExtractor(engine='rule')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 测试文本清洗\\n",
    "sample_html = '''\\n",
    "<html>\\n",
    "<body>\\n",
    "<h1>AI行业周报：大模型竞赛升级</h1>\\n",
    "<p>2024年1月，多家科技巨头发布了新一代大语言模型。</p>\\n",
    "<p>OpenAI发布了GPT-5，Google推出了Gemini Ultra，百度文心一言4.0也正式上线。</p>\\n",
    "<div class=\\"ad\\">广告：点击领取AI课程优惠券</div>\\n",
    "</body>\\n",
    "</html>\\n",
    "'''\\n",
    "\\n",
    "result = cleaner.clean(sample_html)\\n",
    "print(f'标题: {result.title}')\\n",
    "print(f'字数: {result.word_count}')\\n",
    "print(f'质量分: {result.quality_score:.2f}')\\n",
    "print(f'摘要: {result.clean_summary[:100]}...')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 实体识别\\n",
    "text = '''\\n",
    "2024年1月15日，阿里巴巴集团宣布与上海市政府达成战略合作协议，\\n",
    "将在浦东新区投资50亿元建设人工智能研究院。阿里巴巴CEO张勇表示，\\n",
    "这一合作将推动长三角地区的数字经济发展。\\n",
    "'''\\n",
    "\\n",
    "entities = ner.predict(text)\\n",
    "for e in entities:\\n",
    "    print(f'[{e[\\"type\\"]}] {e[\\"text\\"]} (置信度: {e[\\"confidence\\"]:.2f})')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 小结\\n",
    "- 清洗流水线去除HTML标签和广告噪声\\n",
    "- 基于规则的NER可识别基本实体类型\\n",
    "- 连接真实API和数据库后可进行更深度的分析"
   ]
  }
 ],
